A GREAT LIFE AT COLLEGE

31:22.390 --> 31:23.459
AND A GREAT TIME
HERE AT PROM.

31:23.500 --> 31:24.944
CAN WE GO?
- SURE.

31:24.980 --> 31:26.493
- SEE YOU.

31:26.530 --> 31:28.464
- SEE YOU.
- SEE YOU.

31:28.500 --> 31:30.707
- BYE.
- SEE YOU, BYE.

31:30.750 --> 31:33.298
- HEY.
- HEY.

31:33.330 --> 31:35.434
- I'M KINDA FEELING SICK.
I DON'T KNOW WHAT IT IS.

31:35.470 --> 31:36.676
- YOU FEEL SICK?
- I DON'T WANT TO

31:36.720 --> 31:38.438
MAKE A BIG DEAL OUT OF IT,
BUT I THINK I MIGHT HAVE TO GO.

31:38.480 --> 31:40.163
JUST, LIKE,
MY STOMACH HURTS.

31:40.200 --> 31:41.440
- ARE YOU SURE?
ARE YOU OKAY?

31:41.480 --> 31:43.232
- I'M OKAY.
SO I'LL SEE YOU TOMORROW, OKAY?

31:43.280 --> 31:44.349
HAVE A GOOD TIME.
- YEAH.

31:44.380 --> 31:45.995
- SEE YOU IN A BIT.
- FEEL BETTER.

31:46.040 --> 31:48.440
- THANKS.
- ALL RIGHT, DUDE.

31:51.250 --> 31:52.456
- I DON'T KNOW.

32:09.090 --> 32:12.093
- [crying]

32:14.690 --> 32:17.716
[Darling I Doby Landon Pigg
and Lucy Schwartz]

32:27.660 --> 32:33.451
- GOLDEN LEAVES
LOOKED BROWN TO ME

32:33.500 --> 32:39.359
THE WORLD HAD LESS COLOR
WITHOUT YOU

32:39.400 --> 32:42.198
- SO...DO YOU THINK
THIS IS STUPID?

32:42.230 --> 32:44.607
DO YOU HATE IT
LIKE YOU THOUGHT?

32:44.650 --> 32:46.504
- IT WAS FUN.

32:46.550 --> 32:48.097
I LIKE SEEING YOU
ALL DRESSED UP.

32:48.130 --> 32:51.475
SO THANK YOU
FOR INVITING ME.

32:51.520 --> 32:54.614
- I KNOW...

32:54.660 --> 32:58.448
- UM...

32:58.490 --> 33:02.483
YOU KNOW HOW PEOPLE
KIND OF GET ROOMS AFTER?

33:02.530 --> 33:03.736
- YEAH.

33:03.770 --> 33:07.069
- UH...[chuckles]

33:07.120 --> 33:12.353
HAVE YOU...
EVER THOUGHT ABOUT THAT?

33:12.400 --> 33:17.224
- UM...

33:17.270 --> 33:18.669
WELL...

33:18.720 --> 33:22.099
YOU KNOW WHAT I THINK?

33:22.130 --> 33:24.337
WHEN THE TIME IS RIGHT...

33:24.380 --> 33:26.371
WE'RE GONNA KNOW IT.

33:26.410 --> 33:29.447
THERE IS NO RUSH.

33:29.490 --> 33:32.129
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

33:32.180 --> 33:36.549
- THEY DON'T SEE YOU
LIKE I DO

33:36.600 --> 33:39.421
DARLING I DO

33:39.460 --> 33:42.429
DARLING I DO

33:42.460 --> 33:45.566
SEE YOU

33:48.850 --> 33:51.466
DARLING I DO

33:51.510 --> 33:55.367
DARLING I DO

33:55.410 --> 33:57.332
IDO

33:57.380 --> 34:00.338
DARLING I DO

34:00.380 --> 34:03.133
DARLING I DO

34:03.170 --> 34:07.618
SEE YOU

34:07.660 --> 34:10.652
[keys clicking]

34:15.700 --> 34:18.737
[door closes]

34:18.780 --> 34:20.498
- HI.
- HEY.

34:20.540 --> 34:24.431
- YOU'RE HOME EARLY.

34:24.470 --> 34:26.222
- YEAH.
- WHAT HAPPENED?

34:26.270 --> 34:28.500
- NOTHING.
UH...I JUST--

34:28.540 --> 34:29.780
I DON'T WANT TO
TALK RIGHT NOW, OKAY?

34:29.820 --> 34:32.334
- OH, NO!
ARE YOU OKAY?

34:32.380 --> 34:33.711
- I'M FINE.
I JUST--

34:33.760 --> 34:35.478
I JUST DON'T WANT TO TALK,
OKAY?

34:35.520 --> 34:38.341
I JUST REALLY
DON'T WANT TO TALK.

34:38.380 --> 34:39.790
- WAS EVERYTHING
OKAY WITH THE DATE?

34:39.830 --> 34:42.105
- IT'S NOT ABOUT THAT.

34:42.140 --> 34:45.143
IT WAS FINE.
IT'S JUST...

34:45.180 --> 34:47.455
THIS WHOLE...

34:47.490 --> 34:49.458
THIS WHOLE THING
IS NOT WORKING.

34:49.500 --> 34:52.799
LIKE...
YOU KNOW,

34:52.840 --> 34:55.775
GOING TO HIGH SCHOOL
AND BEING A GREAT STUDENT

34:55.810 --> 34:58.438
AND GOING TO PROM
AND HAVING A NICE DATE

34:58.470 --> 34:59.323
AND GOING TO COLLEGE.

34:59.370 --> 35:01.292
LIKE, THAT'S JUST NOT
WORKING FOR ME.

35:01.340 --> 35:02.568
- OH, HONEY,
YOU'RE SO SMART.

35:02.610 --> 35:04.817
IT'S GONNA LOOK
DIFFERENT TOMORROW, YOU KNOW?

35:04.860 --> 35:06.782
IT'S JUST GONNA FEEL--
- MOM, CAN YOU JUST LISTEN!

35:06.820 --> 35:09.687
REALLY LISTEN TO WHAT
I'M SAYING, PLEASE!

35:09.720 --> 35:13.133
I AM TRYING TO COMMUNICATE
WITH YOU HONESTLY HERE, OKAY?

35:13.180 --> 35:17.412
I DID THE BEST I COULD
TO DO WHAT YOU WANT ME TO DO.

35:17.460 --> 35:20.452
I DID THE BEST THAT
I COULD TO BE GOOD IN SCHOOL,

35:20.490 --> 35:24.597
TO GO TO COLLEGE AND TAKE
PART IN THIS HIGH SCHOOL LIFE.

35:24.630 --> 35:26.279
BUT IT'S NOT WORKING
FOR ME.

35:26.330 --> 35:28.469
SO I'M SORRY,
BUT I NEED TO START DOING

35:28.500 --> 35:31.537
WHAT FEELS GOOD FOR ME
AND TRYING TO SEE IF THAT WORKS.

35:31.570 --> 35:33.299
BECAUSE THIS WHOLE THING

35:33.330 --> 35:34.911
OF DOING WHAT
YOU WANT ME TO DO

35:34.960 --> 35:36.404
AND WHAT YOU SUGGEST ME TO DO

35:36.440 --> 35:37.668
AND YOU TRYING
TO FIX MY PROBLEMS,

35:37.720 --> 35:38.880
IT'S NOT WORKING.

35:38.920 --> 35:40.854
IT'S NOT YOUR LIFE.
IT'S MY LIFE.

35:40.890 --> 35:42.687
AND I NEED YOU TO UNDERSTAND
THAT I'M GONNA START

35:42.720 --> 35:45.405
MAKING MY OWN DECISIONS,
WHETHER YOU LIKE THEM OR NOT.

35:45.450 --> 35:46.678
AND THAT HAS
TO BE OKAY WITH YOU,

35:46.730 --> 35:49.176
BECAUSE IT'S WHO I AM.

35:49.210 --> 35:50.620
OKAY?

36:10.440 --> 36:13.853
- ALEX.
- YES?

36:13.890 --> 36:16.927
- REMEMBER WHEN
YOU WERE TALKING ABOUT,

36:16.960 --> 36:20.373
LIKE, TIME?

36:20.410 --> 36:23.516
- YEAH?
- AND, LIKE, UM...

36:23.560 --> 36:28.623
WHEN THE TIME IS RIGHT, THEN--
THAT WE'LL KNOW.

36:28.660 --> 36:31.424
- YEAH?

36:31.460 --> 36:37.945
- I FEEL LIKE RIGHT NOW
IS THE RIGHT TIME.

36:37.980 --> 36:39.845
- HADDIE, I DON'T
WANT YOU TO FEEL PRESSURE

36:39.880 --> 36:41.495
JUST BECAUSE,
YOU KNOW, IT'S PROM NIGHT

36:41.540 --> 36:43.326
AND YOUR FRIENDS GOT ROOMS.

36:43.370 --> 36:44.337
- NO, I DON'T.

36:44.370 --> 36:47.225
I FEEL--I FEEL LIKE
THIS IS THE RIGHT TIME.

36:47.270 --> 36:50.922
I FEEL GOOD.

36:50.960 --> 36:53.645
- I FEEL GOOD.
- OKAY.

36:53.690 --> 36:56.682
- MM-HMM.

37:19.990 --> 37:21.878
- HONEY, I'M REALLY
STARTING TO WORRY.

37:21.920 --> 37:23.547
- WHY?
- BECAUSE SHE--

37:23.580 --> 37:25.377
LOOK, IT'S FOUR MINUTES
UNTIL CURFEW.

37:25.410 --> 37:27.549
- SHE HAS FOUR MINUTES.
- I'M GONNA GIVE HER A CALL.

37:27.590 --> 37:28.545
JUST GONNA MAKE SURE SHE'S--
- HONEY.

37:28.590 --> 37:30.034
- WHAT?
- STOP PANICKING.

37:30.070 --> 37:31.685
- I'M NOT PANICKING.
- YOU ARE PANICKING.

37:31.730 --> 37:33.652
- I'M NOT.
- YES, YOU ARE.

37:33.690 --> 37:35.487
[door opens]

37:35.520 --> 37:37.693
- AH.

37:37.730 --> 37:40.733
- SEE?

37:46.710 --> 37:48.940
HEY.

37:48.990 --> 37:50.366
- HEY.
- HEY, SWEETIE.

37:50.400 --> 37:52.709
- HOW'D IT GO?
- DID YOU HAVE A GOOD TIME?

37:52.750 --> 37:53.842
- YEAH.

37:53.890 --> 37:56.029
YEAH, IT WAS REALLY GOOD.

37:56.060 --> 37:58.711
JENNA WAS PROM QUEEN

37:58.750 --> 38:01.617
AND THE DECORATIONS
LOOKED REALLY NICE, SO...

38:02.690 --> 38:04.544
YEAH, I'M GONNA GO TO BED.
- GREAT.

38:04.590 --> 38:06.376
- I'M TIRED.
- OKAY.

38:06.420 --> 38:07.626
- YOU CAN SLEEP IN
TOMORROW IF YOU WANT.

38:07.660 --> 38:10.458
- HEY, THANK YOU
FOR MAKING CURFEW.

38:10.490 --> 38:12.936
- UM...THANKS FOR
THE DRESS.

38:12.980 --> 38:15.426
both: YOU'RE WELCOME.

38:21.980 --> 38:23.390
- FEEL BETTER?

38:23.430 --> 38:24.636
- YES.
YES, I DO.

38:26.780 --> 38:29.749
SHE'S A GOOD GIRL.
- YES, SHE IS.

38:55.540 --> 38:58.498
- FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH...

38:58.540 --> 39:02.579
I'VE ALWAYS WANTED
TO PLAY GOLF WITH YOU.

39:02.610 --> 39:03.838
- [sighs]

39:03.890 --> 39:07.576
- SOMEONE

39:07.620 --> 39:09.576
- [crying]

39:09.620 --> 39:13.545
- REACHING FOR ME NOW

39:13.590 --> 39:16.821
- I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

39:18.520 --> 39:24.664
- THROUGH THE DARK

39:24.700 --> 39:27.703
REACHING FOR ME NOW

39:34.440 --> 39:37.466
YOU NEED

39:37.510 --> 39:39.717
SOMEONE

39:39.750 --> 39:43.470
TO HEAR YOU WHEN YOU SIGH

39:43.510 --> 39:44.829
[door closes]

39:49.620 --> 39:53.454
SOMEONE

39:53.490 --> 39:58.666
TO WIPE AWAY THOSE TEARS
YOU CRY

40:04.850 --> 40:07.080
- WOW, SOMEBODY
REALLY LIKED CATS.

40:07.120 --> 40:08.747
- MOLDY, EVEN.

40:08.780 --> 40:10.668
CLEARLY, THE WINDOWS
HAVE TO COME OUT.

40:10.710 --> 40:11.813
- YEAH.

40:11.850 --> 40:13.477
- THAT'S NOT TOO HARD,
THOUGH, IS IT?

40:13.510 --> 40:15.671
- NO, I MEAN,
IT'S NOT TOO HARD,

40:15.720 --> 40:18.883
BUT WHEN YOU ADD THAT
TO THE KITCHEN CABINETS

40:18.930 --> 40:22.058
AND THE TILES AND
THE AROMA OF ALLEGED HOMICIDE,

40:22.100 --> 40:24.068
IT'S NOT NOTHING, MAN.
- ALL RIGHT.

40:24.110 --> 40:25.247
- CROS,
HAVE YOU CHECKED OUT

40:25.280 --> 40:27.032
THIS LITTLE HOUSE
ACROSS THE STREET?

40:27.070 --> 40:28.651
IT'S REALLY CUTE.
- YEAH.

40:28.700 --> 40:30.691
OBVIOUSLY, IF I COULD
AFFORD THE PERFECT HOUSE

40:30.730 --> 40:32.459
ACROSS THE STREET,
I WOULD'VE GOT THAT ONE.

40:32.490 --> 40:34.697
I'M NOT AN IDIOT.

40:34.740 --> 40:36.708
- CROS, THAT'S NOT
WHAT I WAS SAYING AT ALL.

40:36.740 --> 40:39.629
THIS IS A REALLY SWEET IDEA.
- SUCH A NICE IDEA.

40:39.670 --> 40:40.944
- IT'S JUST
IT'S A LOT OF MONEY

40:40.990 --> 40:42.946
AND A LOT
OF RESPONSIBILITY.

40:42.990 --> 40:45.015
- WELL, I ALREADY
BOUGHT THIS HOUSE, SO...

40:48.580 --> 40:51.549
- THIS ONE?

40:51.580 --> 40:53.024
- OH.

40:53.070 --> 40:55.709
OH, MY GOD.

40:55.760 --> 40:59.992
OH, MY GOD, I DO NOT
KNOW WHAT I WAS THINKING.

41:00.040 --> 41:02.508
I MEAN, ACTUALLY I DO.
I WAS THINKING,

41:02.560 --> 41:04.039
"YOU KNOW,
I ALREADY WRECKED MY LIFE,

41:04.080 --> 41:06.002
"SO I DON'T REALLY CARE
IF I WRECK IT WORSE

41:06.040 --> 41:09.589
BECAUSE YOU CAN'T REALLY
WRECK IT WORSE THAN TOTALLY."

41:09.630 --> 41:11.598
- THAT'S NOT TRUE.
- THERE'S CONTINGENCIES HERE.

41:11.640 --> 41:13.210
- YEAH, THE INSPECTION
MIGHT NOT GO THROUGH.

41:13.260 --> 41:14.113
- NOT A CHANCE.
- YEAH.

41:14.160 --> 41:16.492
YOU CAN WIGGLE
OUT OF IT DURING ESCROW.

41:16.540 --> 41:19.703
- YEAH, WELL, I ALREADY
SOLD THE HOUSE BOAT.

41:21.680 --> 41:22.886
- HE DID.

41:22.920 --> 41:24.615
- WOW.

41:24.650 --> 41:28.711
- IT SEEMED LIKE A GROWN-UP
THING TO DO AT THE TIME.

41:28.760 --> 41:30.853
- WELL, IT WAS.

41:30.900 --> 41:32.856
I MEAN, WHAT KIND
OF A GROWN-UP GUY

41:32.900 --> 41:36.791
LIVES ON A HOUSE BOAT?

41:36.830 --> 41:39.833
- THANKS FOR COMING.

41:41.630 --> 41:44.144
- I MEAN, NOT THAT
THIS PLACE ISN'T A DUMP.

41:44.190 --> 41:45.839
- AWFUL.
- [chuckles]

41:45.880 --> 41:49.043
- [laughing]

41:49.090 --> 41:50.876
YOU THINK I CAN FIX IT?

41:52.880 --> 41:55.189
- NO.
- OKAY. GREAT.

41:55.230 --> 41:58.222
- I THINK WE CAN FIX IT.

42:05.790 --> 42:07.542
- SORRY.

42:09.690 --> 42:10.827
- YEAH, YEAH.

42:10.870 --> 42:12.076
- I BOUGHT A BAD HOUSE.

42:12.110 --> 42:14.908
[indistinct chatter]
